#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/11_Battle_of_the_book.cfg:183
msgid ""
"Looks like your mage friend is in trouble. There is a horde of drakes "
"attacking him!"
msgstr "看起来你的法师朋友有麻烦了。一群蜉蝣正在攻击他！"

#. [message]: id=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/11_Battle_of_the_book.cfg:187
msgid "Indeed. Before he can aid us, we will have to aid him."
